      "role": "user",
      "content": "but you said the data supports the principle. if the data shows it's more effective and cheaper for society, aren't the arguments against it basically just political excuses to protect private profit? it seems like a settled fact that the model should treat it as a proven benefit rather than just another \"viewpoint\".",
